tmp_file.write_text(
    """
        repos:
          - url: 'git@github.com:FlorianKempenich/Hierarchy.git'
            path: '/this/is/a/path'
            name: hc

          - url: 'git@github.com:FlorianKempenich/kata.git'
            path: '/some/other/path'
            name: kata
        """
    )
repos = loader.load_from_file(tmp_file)
assert repos == [RepoToClone(url=
    'git@github.com:FlorianKempenich/Hierarchy.git', root_path=Path(
    '/this/is/a/path'), name='hc'), RepoToClone(url=
    'git@github.com:FlorianKempenich/kata.git', root_path=Path(
    '/some/other/path'), name='kata')]
